title: Laura Jones And The Gates Of Good And Evil realityarcade.com
description:
Laura Jones And The Gates Of Good And Evil realityarcade.com

The famous adventurer, Laura Jones, receives a letter with news of the discovery of an ancient talisman. It turns out to be one of the keys to the Mystical Gates, preserving the source of sacred powers that affect people all around the world. Laura must protect the portal and keep evil from getting through the Gates. Help her solve adventure puzzles, search for clues, and save the world from the fatal destruction that is a threat to us all!
